28namespace webrtc {
29
30rtc::scoped_refptr<PeerConnectionFactoryInterface> CreatePeerConnectionFactory(
31 rtc::Thread* network_thread,
32 rtc::Thread* worker_thread,
33 rtc::Thread* signaling_thread,
34 rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioDeviceModule> default_adm,
35 rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioEncoderFactory> audio_encoder_factory,
36 rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioDecoderFactory> audio_decoder_factory,
37 std::unique_ptr<VideoEncoderFactory> video_encoder_factory,
38 std::unique_ptr<VideoDecoderFactory> video_decoder_factory,
39 rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioMixer> audio_mixer,
40 rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioProcessing> audio_processing,
41 AudioFrameProcessor* audio_frame_processor) {
42 PeerConnectionFactoryDependencies dependencies;
43 dependencies.network_thread = network_thread;
44 dependencies.worker_thread = worker_thread;
45 dependencies.signaling_thread = signaling_thread;
46 dependencies.task_queue_factory = CreateDefaultTaskQueueFactory();
47 dependencies.call_factory = CreateCallFactory();
48 dependencies.event_log_factory = std::make_unique<RtcEventLogFactory>(
49 dependencies.task_queue_factory.get());
50 dependencies.trials = std::make_unique<webrtc::FieldTrialBasedConfig>();
51
52 cricket::MediaEngineDependencies media_dependencies;
53 media_dependencies.task_queue_factory = dependencies.task_queue_factory.get();
54 media_dependencies.adm = std::move(default_adm);
55 media_dependencies.audio_encoder_factory = std::move(audio_encoder_factory);
56 media_dependencies.audio_decoder_factory = std::move(audio_decoder_factory);
57 media_dependencies.audio_frame_processor = audio_frame_processor;
58 if (audio_processing) {
59 media_dependencies.audio_processing = std::move(audio_processing);
60 } else {
61 media_dependencies.audio_processing = AudioProcessingBuilder().Create();
62 }
63 media_dependencies.audio_mixer = std::move(audio_mixer);
64 media_dependencies.video_encoder_factory = std::move(video_encoder_factory);
65 media_dependencies.video_decoder_factory = std::move(video_decoder_factory);
66 media_dependencies.trials = dependencies.trials.get();
67 dependencies.media_engine =
68 cricket::CreateMediaEngine(std::move(media_dependencies));
69
70 return CreateModularPeerConnectionFactory(std::move(dependencies));
71}
72
73} // namespace webrtc
